      "description": "Offered is a driver-spec 2008 BMW M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system, delivering an 8,400 RPM redline. The power is managed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its composure with aluminum multi-link suspension and cross-drilled compound rotors. This example presents in strong mechanical health with a service history reflecting proactive maintenance of the rod bearings and throttle actuators. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the structural integrity and powertrain performance remain sharp for the discerning enthusiast.",
