      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-cared for, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next big adventure right away! It drives beautifully and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp. I\u2019d love for this to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have\u2014feel free to shoot me a message if you have any questions!",
